  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:10px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/HibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5Bf68Hzehf94hQSRZRVAcywLjPC3avecjUXLEZMEEPheoeb2JJM7zRQIA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"558\" data-cropsely2=\"234\" data-imgfileid=\"100012489\" data-ratio=\"0.4190371991247265\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1828\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4058326f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5Bf68Hzehf94hQSRZRVAcywLjPC3avecjUXLEZMEEPheoeb2JJM7zRQIA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">嗨大家好！我是阿真！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">了解我的人都知道，虽然我混得不怎么样，但是我的朋友都牛逼且靠谱，前几天藏师傅（@歸藏的AI工具箱）跟我说有个大佬有新产品要上了，这个情况我都是二话不说直接冲的。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.30925925925925923\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dee70f16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfySx4NiaWjt1ct2BTHjYIa2iaAcqMZpiapsxMdnYsXE2xYATiapRnCgho2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个产品就是 Dokie 。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 生成 PPT 的工具太多了，但大多数给我的感觉要么是一句话生成了一个好看但不好改不好用的 PPT ，要么就是一次完成要修改起来比较麻烦，或者是是整体的风格不够一致，正式场合使用总觉得差那么一口气。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI PPT 工具我写到的比较少，因为我要求还是挺高的，大多数生成效果都让我不太满意。但Dokie确实是我目前用过的 AI PPT 工具里，生成效果最接近能直接用的，包括商业级使用。它对上传内容的理解、排版设计的水准，还有后续修改的灵活度，都是很不错的，尤其是修改这块。当然也不是完美无缺，后续我们细说。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接在这里👉&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://dokie.ai/\" target=\"_blank\">https://dokie.ai/</a></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">主页长这样👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49074074074074076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9661fed4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfoRopmkhRJiaibOsTzoicc0j2YZquS6pn9F6PyYajwq8PNcdhXQ7BatYkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border:1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">基础生成</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我先试了最基础的，让它一句话生成。直接给了一个比较笼统的主题，看它怎么理解和呈现。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的要求是：把《西游记》做成商业计划书。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">接着会进入这样的页面，左边是你可以直接聊天提出修改意见和发送附件的地方，右边是 PPT 的相关信息设置，包括主题场景、页数以及是否通过智能文本与图片搜索优化大纲。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf7077b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfK49H0H8RLOYPDA0CWZedLnMuB0ibGZmr8g5E0JkqwicaskO9K5PGjwAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">点击全部主题还可以设置自定义主题。我试过了，使用 PDF 导入的速度会更快👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3cb26db5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfUzicZD6Zb7yPLPbKyIJJHx25CYt7BDtLpJn4VzsUswMic4icZ8PNXHpKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2cf12e0b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfBZ41G4dexgdkW0XMkBnGhzFK3noiccfSLUzibbWLDeeGLW2th1fia5wGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次我先选一个模板，直接让它生成试试看。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">它首先会生成大纲，生成以后，我左边对话那里告诉它需要添加的内容，它会直接添加在符合逻辑的位置。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6962962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e4c893d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfyBgGFCS6l30gD7Iug0ZBiccnPDmuBibLuriantf2jyruibSGqSFTE4bqow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后我点击了【确认并生成】。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成速度还是挺快的。感兴趣可以去看一下完整的PPT效果：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 92, 212);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://dokie.ai/presentation/share/KL6XaNmw1Ylg\" target=\"_blank\">https://dokie.ai/presentation/share/KL6XaNmw1Ylg</a></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">出来的效果第一眼就觉得挺舒服的。整个排版方式确实是根据我的内容去决定每一页怎么排版，没有生硬地套模板。比如页面信息多了就会自动用分栏，有些页面重点突出，它还会单独做大字强调，整体的逻辑也很通顺，图表和信息内容的搭配非常合理。这是他们说的以内容为中心的设计，跟纯套模板的感觉确实不一样。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我这里选择一些放一下👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e36bb62&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfuPzSDl3xSIRAY3HiaZ8uR48TS6hHns4aaV6WUVlYBeJR7NSYGXoyL2g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2960d0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiactA81dzORBHWhAqrQ7y5BfpENkFPUWbqMGQHic0m8iataIibyHLRwlZlDHee2k4Ownl3HJedibnFywnA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgb(241, 240, 253) 2px 2px 4px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\